WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.520
I know what I want.

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:06.279
I want to be able to
talk to my wife again.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.080
The way we used to
talk to each other.

00:00:10.319 --> 00:00:14.279
Like there was no one else
in the world except us.

00:00:14.919 --> 00:00:18.200
How are you gonna do that?

